  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    International Driving Permits (IDPs): the facts
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
    <div class="column-third">
      <nav role="navigation" class="gem-c-translation-nav  " aria-label="Translations">
    <ul class="gem-c-translation-nav__list">
        <li class="gem-c-translation-nav__list-item">
            <span lang="en">English</span>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-translation-nav__list-item">
            <a hreflang="cy" lang="cy" rel="alternate" class="gem-c-translation-nav__link " href="/government/news/international-driving-permits-idps-the-facts.cy">Cymraeg</a>
        </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  </div>

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    An IDP is a permit that may be needed, in addition to your driving licence, if you plan to drive abroad.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="column-two-thirds metadata-column">
